<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>HYMN OF ADVENT</B></FONT></H2>
<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>"A CLEAR VOICE DISPELS THE DARKNESS"</B></FONT></H2>
<H3><PRE>
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  A clear voice
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    dispels the darkness with its echoes,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    drives away the anguish.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Jesus shines forth!
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                         Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Let the torpid soul awake
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                    E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    and no longer creep along the ground.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    A new star arises!
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Behold
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    he sends us a Lamb,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                       Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    to freely pay our debts.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                           E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Let us go to him with tears,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                            Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    let us all ask him for pardon,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">       Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    so that,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    when he appears glorious,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                   Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    in his second coming,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                              E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    and fills the world with terror,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                     Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    he may in pity protect us.
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  This is why
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                  Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    we sing this praise
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                    E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    to the Father, the Son and the Spirit
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    that they may live,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Amen!
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     Dm
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    This s why
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                  Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    we sing this praise
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                                    E
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    to the Father, the Son and the Spirit
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    that they may live,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">     Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    Amen!
